@startuml
title ModelAsset -> build -> instantiate

left to right direction
'top to bottom direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing true
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam defaultFontName Yu Gothic UI
skinparam defaultFontSize 18
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 24
  BorderColor black
  BackgroundColor #f7fbff
  FontColor black
}
skinparam ArrowColor black
skinparam ranksep 20
skinparam nodesep 20

rectangle "glTF / GLB" as Gltf
rectangle "Collada" as Collada
rectangle "imported JSON" as ImportedJson
rectangle "ModelAsset\nCPU 側の共通データ" as ModelAsset
rectangle "validate" as Validate
rectangle "build()" as Build
rectangle "モデル\nGPU共有バッファ" as Runtime
rectangle "instantiate() -> A" as InstA
rectangle "instantiate() -> B" as InstB
rectangle "instantiate() -> C" as InstC

Gltf --> ModelAsset
Collada --> ModelAsset
ImportedJson --> ModelAsset
ModelAsset --> Validate
ModelAsset --> Build
Build --> Runtime
Runtime -down-> InstA
Runtime -down-> InstB
Runtime -down-> InstC

note top of Gltf
入力形式
end note

note top of Runtime
build は 1 回
必要な数だけインスタンスを作る
end note
@enduml
